PLEASE

Russia and the enemy can look and see details in photos and conversations that put ukrainias and freedom fighters in danger. 

They can get geolocations, meta data, facial recognition, and info from photos that you may have never considered. 

Your pic alone might not be enough but the enemy has lots of info and can use your pic to solve a puzzle. 

You might think "sauce" on a cool pic or story is nice but so does the enemy. 

You might think a simple pic of a "tank" or group of guys without other info is harmless but the enemy can see other photos and comments and piece things together. 

ALSO IT DOESNT MATTER IF THE PIC IS OLD OR FROM ANOTHER SITE, ITS STILL SPREADING VALUABLE INFO THE ENEMY CAN FIND AND USE. 

DONT LET IMGUR HELP RUSSIA AND HURT OUR FORCES. 

Please stop helping Russia guys! 

Ask yourself before posting... could this help putin find/hunt/kill/or workaround ukrainian forces?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e5rs1Uo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OvRRti9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kpzEKgv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xzcaRw3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jCtcgJq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xUlDwnu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[icutyouinyoursleep]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>